'''馬修·詹姆斯·托馬斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Matthew James Thomas'''}}<ref>[http://ibdb.com/person.php?id=488509 "Matthew James Thomas"] {{Wayback|url=http://ibdb.com/person.php?id=488509 |date=20150721234754 }}. www.IBDB.com. Internet Broadway Database. Retrieved 16 April 2015.</ref>；{{bd|1988年|3月3日}}），為[[英國|英國]]籍男演員及歌手，同時也兼具電視、喜劇演員，
因演出電視節目的《[[舞·青春|舞·青春]]》中Jez Tyler一角而眾人所知。

==生平==
托馬斯出生於英國白金漢郡，他受訓於西爾維亞青年戲劇學校在倫敦<ref>Evans, Suzy (26 March 2013). [http://www.backstage.com/interview/6-acting-lessons-pippins-matthew-james-thomas/ "6 Acting Lessons From 'Pippin's' Matthew James Thomas"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.backstage.com/interview/6-acting-lessons-pippins-matthew-james-thomas/ |date=20160306201345 }}. Backstage. Retrieved 16 April 2015.</ref>，後來在戲劇藝術的義大利肯迪演藝學院也在倫敦<ref>Barrett, Hannah (1 July 2013). [http://www.broadwaymasterchat.com/2013/07/matthew-james-thomas-is-extraordinary.html "Matthew James Thomas is EXTRAORDINARY"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.broadwaymasterchat.com/2013/07/matthew-james-thomas-is-extraordinary.html |date=20160305042724 }}. Broadway Master Chat. Retrieved 16 April 2015.</ref>。他主要是在英格蘭的白金漢郡長大。<ref>Moore, John (20 September 2014). [http://www.denvercenter.org/blog-posts/news-center/2014/09/20/the-%27pippin%27-profiles-matthew-james-thomas-on-being-shot-out-of-a-cannon "The 'Pippin' Profiles: Matthew James Thomas on being shot out of a cannon"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.denvercenter.org/blog-posts/news-center/2014/09/20/the-%27pippin%27-profiles-matthew-james-thomas-on-being-shot-out-of-a-cannon |date=20160629194839 }}. [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Denver_Center_for_the_Performing_Arts Denver Center for the Performing Arts] {{Wayback|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Denver_Center_for_the_Performing_Arts |date=20210309094729 }}. Retrieved 16 April 2015.</ref>

